pride_menu:
    clear_dialog
    choice:
        "The hustle and bustle is almost overwhelming, but there are far too many sensations for a little lady like yourself to ignore."
        "[Take a look at the stall selling stuffed animals]" if (!= $data.pride.stuffedAnimal true):
            play sound footsteps
            "The stall contains a large selection of toy animals. They're all quite cute, but three in particular catch your eye."
            if (< $stats.money.value 5):
                "Unfortunately they're all too expensive for you, so you have to awkwardly avoid their sellers eye and duck the fuck out."
                jump pride_menu
            if (objective_started? writer pride):
                talk lovely talk "A though occurs darling, perhaps your paramour would appreciate a present?"
            clear_dialog
            choice:
                "The stuffed toys all look so soft... you feel almost compelled to buy and clutch one."
                "[BUY - Stuffed 'Transexual Scandinavian Shark' - Five Anglian Pounds]" if (>= $stats.money.value 5):
                    set data.pride.stuffedAnimal true
                    add_stat money -5
                    add_item plushShark 1
                    play sound coins
                    "A comically huge soft toy shark. It's incredibly unthreatening, which is impressive for a shark. It stares at you with its toothy, faintly Nordic smile."
                    if (objective_started? writer pride):
                        "The Pulp Writer peers over at you, a single eyebrow raised in curiosity."
                        clear_dialog
                        choice:
                            talk writer talk "What have you got there, Ghost? A thing?"
                            "\\"Sharky.\\" [Waggle the shark about and grin]":
                                choice:
                                    talk writer talk "Ah, sharky... I see..."
                                    "\\"It's for you! Here!\\" [Give it to The Pulp Writer]":
                                        add data.pride.writerEnjoyment 1
                                        talk writer talk "O- oh! Goodness. Thank you, Ghost. It's very uh, sweet?"
                                        clear_dialog
                                        "She smiles, very softly. The beginning of a blush."
                                        if (roll pride_menu_sheep lovely 40):
                                            talk lovely talk "She has not received a present for a very long time, and she does quite like sharks. Grey and mean, with a big bite. She used to remind herself of one, when she was less dozy."
                                        else:
                                            wait 1000
                                    "[Keep it]":
                                        add_item plushShark 1
                                        unlock_achievement plushie
                                        if (roll pride_menu_toy_keep_lovely lovely 40):
                                            talk lovely talk "She's a little sad. Part of her thought it might be for her. She'll never admit this though. Not even under waterboarding."
                                        else:
                                            wait 1000
                    else:
                        unlock_achievement plushie
                        add_item plushShark 1
                "[BUY - Stuffed 'Singing Bird' - Five Anglian Pounds]" if (>= $stats.money.value 5):
                    set data.pride.stuffedAnimal true
                    set data.pride.stuffedBird true
                    add_stat money -5
                    play sound coins
                    "A sparrow, it's round and dumb looking, just as a stuffed bird toy should be. It's not particularly soft, there's an extremely obvious mechanical device sewn inside of it."
                    if (roll pride_menu_bird_orb orb 40):
                        talk orb talk "It uses a uranium fission device to produce sound from some kind of wax cylinder. It's horrendously dangerous, while also being needlessly over engineered."
                    else:
                        wait 1000
                    if (objective_started? writer pride):
                        clear_dialog
                        choice:
                            "The Pulp Writer looks mortified that you might be about to give her this as a present."
                            "[Squeeze the soft toy] \\"Look, it makes a sound!\\"":
                                play sound plushbird
                                "The bird sings its song. A tinny <span class='writtenText'>'peep. peep. peep. peep. peep. peep. peep. peep.'</span> followed by an unpleasant record scratch."
                                choice:
                                    "It peeps slightly too many times, and slightly too loud to be comfortable. The Pulp Writer looks aghast."
                                    "\\"It's for you! Here!\\" [Give it to The Pulp Writer]":
                                        add data.pride.writerEnjoyment 1
                                        talk writer talk "M... Mercy..."
                                        clear_dialog
                                        "She snaps herself out of 'warplane caught in search light' mode."
                                        clear_dialog
                                        talk writer talk "Ahem. Merci, Ghost."
                                        talk writer talk "I uh, I like it very much."
                                        clear_dialog
                                        "She gives you an incredibly pained smile, which is tinted with the beginnings of a blush."
                                        if (roll pride_menu_bird_lovely lovely 40):
                                            talk lovely talk "She hates how much she secretly really likes the present. She has not received one for a very long time."
                                        else:
                                            wait 1000
                                    "[Keep it]":
                                        unlock_achievement plushie
                                        add_item plushBird 1
                                        if (roll pride_menu_toy_keep_lovely lovely 40):
                                            talk lovely talk "She's a little sad. Part of her thought it might be for her. She'll never admit this though. Not even under waterboarding."
                                        else:
                                            wait 1000
                    else:
                        unlock_achievement plushie
                        add_item plushBird 1
                "[BUY - Stuffed 'Fully Fungible Sensible Sheep' - Five Anglian Pounds]" if (>= $stats.money.value 5):
                    set data.pride.stuffedAnimal true
                    add_stat money -5
                    play sound coins
                    "A soft sheep, with real wool. It's incredibly stupid looking, in a very adorable way, like you."
                    if (objective_started? writer pride):
                        "The Pulp Writer peers at you, a single eyebrow raised in curiosity."
                        clear_dialog
                        choice:
                            talk writer talk "Wauw, what have you got there, Ghost? A thing?"
                            "\\"It's a sheep! Baa baa!\\" [Waggle the sheep about to imply it's the one going <span class='writtenText'>'baa baa'</span>]":
                                choice:
                                    talk writer talk "I... yes, I suppose it is a sheep, isn't it."
                                    "\\"It's for you! Here!\\" [Give it to The Pulp Writer]":
                                        add data.pride.writerEnjoyment 1
                                        talk writer talk "O- oh! Goodness. Thank you, Ghost. It's very uh, sweet?"
                                        clear_dialog
                                        "She smiles, very softly. The beginning of a blush."
                                        if (roll pride_menu_sheep lovely 40):
                                            talk lovely talk "She has not received a present for a very long time."
                                        else:
                                            wait 1000
                                    "[Keep it]":
                                        unlock_achievement plushie
                                        add_item plushSheep 1
                                        if (roll pride_menu_toy_keep_lovely lovely 40):
                                            talk lovely talk "She's a little sad. Part of her thought it might be for her. She'll never admit this though. Not even under waterboarding."
                                        else:
                                            wait 1000
                    else:
                        unlock_achievement plushie
                        add_item plushSheep 1
                "<span class='prompt'>[[MOVE ON]]</span>":
