                        else:
                            "The Pulp Writer watches you drink. She's distracted by your throat."
                        clear_dialog
            if (<= $data.pride.drinksDrunk 3):
                "You empty the glass bottle. It was nice, but your tummy hurts a little. That's okay, soft drinks always do this."
            if (== $data.pride.drinksDrunk 4):
                "Your tummy hurts a LOT."
                clear_dialog
                talk orb talk "You should probably stop drinking dandelion and burdock, Ghost. You're upsetting your tummy."
            if (>= $data.pride.drinksDrunk 5):
                clear_dialog
                "You empty the glass bottle, and immediately fill it back up again. You're throwing up five bottles worth of soft drink. The bottle reaches it's maximum capacity and begins spraying out into your own face, it's so disgusting."
                if (objective_started? writer pride):   
                    clear_dialog
                    "The Pulp Writer is aghast."
                    clear_dialog
                    talk writer talk "Sacrebleu..."
                clear_dialog
                choice:
                    "Your stomach collapses from the sudden change in pressure, and your entire body crumples in on itself like a crushed can."
                    "[Try to scream]":
                        clear_dialog
                        "It is too late to scream, you are dead."
                        unlock_achievement death_drink
